{
  "id": "548b0203-87d4-4b93-9cd6-2320638ac502",
  "name": "IdiamPro - Bootstrap Plan",
  "rootNodeId": "root-bootstrap",
  "nodes": {
    "root-bootstrap": {
      "id": "root-bootstrap",
      "name": "IdiamPro - Bootstrap Plan",
      "content": "<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 2026-07-02</p><p></p><p><strong>Overall: 99% complete (159/160 tasks) — BETA LIVE</strong></p><pre><code>█████████████████████████████░</code></pre><p></p><p><strong>By category:</strong></p><p>Documents &amp; drafts:     100% <code>████████████████████████</code> 15/15</p><p>Code changes:            100% <code>████████████████████████</code> 38/38</p><p>Decision docs:          100% <code>████████████████████████</code> 5/5</p><p>Bug fixes:             100% <code>████████████████████████</code> 2/2</p><p>Awaiting your decisions: 0% <code>░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░</code> 0/5</p><p>External / user-only:    25% <code>██████░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░</code> 3/12</p><p>Post-launch (deferred):   0% <code>░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░░</code> 0/10</p><p></p><p>━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━</p><p>The IdiamPro Bootstrap Plan centers around a lean startup methodology, prioritizing validation and organic growth over initial funding. The core strategy is to build a Minimum Viable Product (MVP) focused on a single, high-value feature set that directly addresses a specific pain point for the target audience. This MVP should be readily demonstrable and usable, enabling early adopters to provide valuable feedback. Marketing efforts will primarily rely on free or low-cost channels, such as content marketing (blog posts, tutorials), social media engagement, and participation in relevant online communities. The plan emphasizes iterative development based on user feedback and usage data, constantly refining the product to better meet market needs. Revenue generation will be prioritized early on, with a focus on a simple, easy-to-understand pricing model. The key milestones include: 1) MVP Launch: Releasing the initial version of IdiamPro with core features. 2) Early Adopter Acquisition: Securing a small group of engaged users who provide feedback. 3) Revenue Validation: Generating enough revenue to cover basic operating costs. 4) Scalable Growth: Expanding marketing efforts and feature set based on validated demand and profitability. This bootstrap approach minimizes risk and maximizes learning, allowing for a more sustainable and resilient business in the long run.</p><p></p><div code=\"flowchart TD\n    A[Identify Core Problem &amp; Target Audience] --&gt; B{Build MVP (Minimum Viable Product)};\n    B --&gt; C[Launch MVP];\n    C --&gt; D{Low-Cost Marketing &amp; Community Engagement};\n    D --&gt; E[Gather User Feedback &amp; Usage Data];\n    E --&gt; F{Iterate &amp; Improve Product};\n    F --&gt; G{Monitor Revenue &amp; Growth Metrics};\n    G --&gt; H{Profitable?};\n    H -- Yes --&gt; I[Scale Marketing &amp; Development];\n    H -- No --&gt; A;\n    I --&gt; G;\" data-mermaid-block=\"\" data-mermaid-code=\"flowchart TD\n    A[Identify Core Problem &amp; Target Audience] --&gt; B{Build MVP (Minimum Viable Product)};\n    B --&gt; C[Launch MVP];\n    C --&gt; D{Low-Cost Marketing &amp; Community Engagement};\n    D --&gt; E[Gather User Feedback &amp; Usage Data];\n    E --&gt; F{Iterate &amp; Improve Product};\n    F --&gt; G{Monitor Revenue &amp; Growth Metrics};\n    G --&gt; H{Profitable?};\n    H -- Yes --&gt; I[Scale Marketing &amp; Development];\n    H -- No --&gt; A;\n    I --&gt; G;\"></div><p></p><p></p><p>A practical roadmap for launching IdiamPro as a solo developer with minimal upfront investment. This plan focuses on building momentum before spending money, validating market demand, and scaling only when revenue supports it.</p>",
      "type": "root",
      "parentId": null,
      "childrenIds": [
        "pm-session-notes",
        "project-roadmap",
        "bootstrap-checklist",
        "phase-1",
        "phase-2",
        "phase-3",
        "phase-4",
