    "cl-compliance": {
      "id": "cl-compliance",
      "name": "App Store Compliance",
      "content": "<p><strong>Required before App Store submission (see Section 11 for details)</strong></p><p></p><p><strong>CRITICAL (Blockers):</strong></p><ul data-type=\"taskList\"><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"true\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\" checked=\"checked\"></label><div><p>Implement AI Consent Dialog — <em>Done 2026-03-22: consent dialog on first AI use, names Gemini/OpenAI/AssemblyAI</em></p></div></li><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Implement In-App Purchases (RevenueCat or StoreKit 2) — <em>or ship beta free</em></p></div></li><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"true\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\" checked=\"checked\"></label><div><p>Create Privacy Policy page — <em>Done 2026-03-22: hosted at /privacy</em></p></div></li><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Configure App Privacy Nutrition Labels in App Store Connect</p></div></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>HIGH PRIORITY:</strong></p><ul data-type=\"taskList\"><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Rotate API keys before public release</p></div></li><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Set API keys in Vercel dashboard environment variables</p></div></li><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Add per-user rate limiting on API routes</p></div></li><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Bundle Google Fonts locally (remove external preconnect)</p></div></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>RECOMMENDED:</strong></p><ul data-type=\"taskList\"><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Consider static export for iOS (offline support)</p></div></li><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Check SDK privacy manifests (Xcode will flag)</p></div></li><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Test on physical iOS device</p></div></li><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Prepare App Store listing assets</p></div></li></ul>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "bootstrap-checklist",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isCollapsed": false,
      "prefix": "3.7"
    },
    "cl-marketing": {
      "id": "cl-marketing",
      "name": "Marketing & Outreach",
      "content": "<p><strong>Pre-launch and launch marketing tasks</strong></p><p></p><ul data-type=\"taskList\"><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Identify target influencers (productivity / PKM YouTubers)</p></div></li><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Prepare influencer outreach emails</p></div></li><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Create demo video / walkthrough</p></div></li><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Write Product Hunt listing copy</p></div></li><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Prepare beta tester onboarding materials</p></div></li><li data-type=\"taskItem\" data-checked=\"false\"><label><input type=\"checkbox\"></label><div><p>Set up feedback collection system</p></div></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Launch-story cross-reference (added 2026-06-06):</strong> The launch story now includes a forward-looking \"From outline to YouTube video — coming soon (v1.1)\" callout on the marketing homepage, in the User Guide, and in the help chat. The video generation work itself stays deferred (chapter 17 — Video generation feasibility + phased plan), but the customer expectation is set now so the v1 launch has a roadmap story instead of a \"this is all there is\" framing. Beta testers get early access to the v1.1 MVP. This influences influencer outreach copy and Product Hunt listing copy — both should mention \"and YouTube video export coming in v1.1\" without overpromising.</p>",
      "type": "document",
      "parentId": "bootstrap-checklist",
      "childrenIds": [],
      "isCollapsed": false,
      "prefix": "3.8"
    },
